<div class="details">
  <%= image_tag("splash-details.jpg", class:"img_top") %>
  <div class="ttcol_lt">
    <h3 class="ff_title fc_2 fontawesome-info-sign"> The Details</h3>
    <%= image_tag("details-block.png", class:"details_block") %>
  </div>

  <div class="ttcol_rt">    
    <div class="details_section">
      <h3 class="ff_title fc_2 maki-airport"> How to Get There</h3>
      <p> If you plan on flying in, PVD is only 30 minutes from Mink Meadow. BOS will likely offer more options and cheaper travel, and is 1.5 hours away. </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> PVD </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> BOS </p>
    </div>
    <div class="details_section">
      <h3 class="ff_title fc_2 maki-lodging"> Where to Stay</h3>
      <p> Since we're so close to the beach, the funnest (and cheapest!) option is to stay at one of the many rental vacation houses in the area: </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> <a href="http://www.homeaway.com/search/keywords:Narragansett+area%2C+Rhode+Island"> HomeAway </a> </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> <a href="http://www.vrbo.com/vacation-rentals/usa/rhode-island/narragansett"> VRBO </a> </p> 
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> <a href="https://www.airbnb.com/s/Narragansett--RI"> AirBnB </a> </p>
      <p> In case you want to stay at a hotel, here are the ones we recommend: </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> <a href="http://hamptoninn3.hilton.com/en/hotels/rhode-island/hampton-inn-south-kingstown-newport-area-NPTSKHX/index.html"> Hampton Inn </a> </p>
      <p class="fontawesome-double-angle-right indent"> <a href="http://www.ihg.com/holidayinn/hotels/us/en/south-kingstown/sknri/hoteldetail"> Holiday Inn </a> </p>
    </div>
    <div class="details_section">
      <h3 class="ff_title fc_2 maki-swimming"> What to Do</h3>
      <p> There's a ton to see and do in Rhode Island and the surrounding states, especially in the summer.  Stay local to enjoy the Newport Mansions, the Narragansett Beaches, and state capital of providence.  Or, take a trip out to Boston, Cape Cod, or New York City - all are within a few hours of driving.  </p>
      <p> <%= link_to 'learn more...', ri_path, class: "ff_read right"%>  </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>